we need some test/schema validating we have entity metadata in mcdata. Maybe something you can help with @ItsDrike As in enforcing the presence of metadataKeys in the data? The schema currently has that as an optional key, and minecraft-data is missing it in various versions, so if you wanted to enforce that, it would need to be added into all versions where it's missing. That's a lot of versions. Versions missing metadataKeys information in entities.json for at least one entity entry
